The evidence with the title 'More tax deceptions - factcheck.org ' says Aug 8, 2008  ... John McCain 2008 ad: "painful". Announcer: life in the spotlight must be grand, but for the rest of us times are tough. Obama voted to raise taxes on people making just $42,000. He promises more taxes on small business, seniors, your life savings, your family. Painful taxes, hard choices for your budget. 
